###  Environment Variables
Create a `.env` file in the root directory and populate it with the following required credentials:

```bash
# LLM Configuration
OPENAI_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1
OPENAI_API_KEY=ollama
LOCAL_LLM_MODEL=phi3
LOCAL_LLM_FILE_PATH="models/Phi-3-mini-4k-instruct-q4.gguf"

# Database Configuration
SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_url_here
SUPABASE_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here
SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET=your_supabase_jwt_secret_here

# Messaging Configuration
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_twilio_sid_here
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_token_here
TWILIO_SANDBOX_NUMBER=+14155238886

# Security Settings
SMS_ALERT_SECRET=your_secret_password_here
# Set DISABLE_TWILIO_SIGNATURE=true ONLY for local development
DISABLE_TWILIO_SIGNATURE=false